{"type":"message","id":"624164d5","parentId":"da3c52a6","timestamp":"2026-05-09T10:53:58.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, backup created. Now let me plan the fixes:\n\n**Issue 1: Chat History - compaction is already set to 8000 keep + 4000 reserve. But there's no `maxHistory` or `compactAfter` setting that limits the number of messages sent. The compaction only kicks in when context gets large, but the system doesn't have a hard limit on how many messages get included. I should add a compaction trigger - something like \"compactAfter: 10\" to ensure history is compressed every 10 turns, not just when tokens are high.\n\n**Issue 2: Tool Output Persistence - This is a code practice issue, not a config issue. The system can't automatically purge tool outputs from context. I need to ensure the AGENTS.md has a clear rule about this.\n\n\n**Issue 3: System Prompt Bloat - The system prompts are loaded from workspace files, not injected into the API call. The AGENTS.md is 292 lines (~13KB), SOUL.md is 71 lines (~4KB), and MEMORY.md is 233 lines (~23KB) - that's substantial overhead for every prompt. I should trim these down significantly, especially AGENTS.md which has plenty of redundant protocol descriptions.\n\nFor the fix, I'll focus on reducing the line counts. AGENTS.md needs to drop from 292 to around 80 lines by removing verbose protocol descriptions and keeping only core operational rules. SOUL.md can compress from 71 to about 30 lines. MEMORY.md is trickier since it's long-term memory, but it shouldn't be in the system prompt at all - that should be handled through retrieval instead.\n\n**Issue 4: Bridge Logic - The relay scripts are straightforward Python polling scripts, so there's no embedded loop logic to worry about. The real optimization would be implementing a character/word threshold so short messages skip unnecessary processing and go straight to the main model instead. I'll start implementing these fixes now.\n","thinkingSignature":"8b5d33d039260c6f3f8b953fb675d0b08c5b3097ebf7f92a583a793f6c9ff456"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nเจ้านายครับ 🧑🏼‍💻 ผมสแกนเสร็จแล้ว เจอปัญหา 4 จุด เริ่มแก้เลยครับ\n\n## สรุปผลสแกน\n\n| # | หัวข้อ | สถานะ | ปัญหา |\n|---|--------|-------|-------|\n| 1 | Chat History | ⚠️ กึ่งโอเค | compaction มีแต่ไม่มี `compactAfter` จำกัดจำนวน turn |\n| 2 | Tool Output Persistence | ❌ ต้องแก้โค้ด | ไม่มี rule ใน AGENTS.md |\n| 3 | System Prompt | ❌ เยิ่นเย้อมาก | AGENTS.md 292 lines, MEMORY.md 233 lines ส่งทุกครั้ง |\n| 4 | Bridge Logic | ⚠️ กึ่งโอเค | รองรับ short bypass แล้วแต่ยังไม่ชัดเจนในโค้ด |\n\nเริ่มแก้ทีละจุ","index":1}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38241,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778323973700,"responseId":"064e4508215e666ac3e0a87155f5dff7"}}
