{"type":"message","id":"3ba5abfa","parentId":"609d35f3","timestamp":"2026-05-09T11:41:46.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"เจ้านายสั่งเริ่มแล้ว เริ่มทำทีละจุดเลยครับ","thinkingSignature":"bcc8ebede45015e49fbbbd24986d23df72273193a957ca350b1dd0b9d55ac8ff"},{"type":"text","text":"เริ่มเลยครับ 🧑🏼‍💻\n\n**แผนสั้นๆ:**\n1. เพิ่ม `compactAfter` ใน config → จำกัด turn history\n2. เพิ่ม rule ล้าง tool output ใน AGENTS.md\n3. ตัด AGENTS.md ให้กระชับ\n4. เพิ่ม short-bypass logic ใน bridge\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0rtl31reg0p8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config set agents.defaults.compaction --json '{\"keepRecentTokens\": 8000, \"reserveTokens\": 4000, \"compactAfter\": 15}'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":203,"output":222,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":50338,"totalTokens":50763,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778326896661,"responseId":"064e507437859b5d043c008b958fad6a"}}
